g.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dcx6nq_vfdLo%23t%3D21s&d=DLcSJ3at4d3q9zJfdG0PmZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=c1357202\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cx6nq_vfdLo#t=21s</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zBDo0FmGyF0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzBDo0FmGyF0&d=DLcSJ3at4d3q9zJfdG0PmZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=c521afcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zBDo0FmGyF0</a><br />\n<br />\n泡菜都有<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=owuJtbFSG6Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DowuJtbFSG6Y&d=DLcSJ3at4d3q9zJfdG0PmZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=4673a599\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=owuJtbFSG6Y</a><br />\n<br />\nNBA又有<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lihyke3XzfU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLihyke3XzfU&d=DLcSJ3at4d3q9zJfdG0PmZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=f356f74b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lihyke3XzfU</a><br />\n<br />\n美式足球都有<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sSxsU-nkBUk#t=25s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsSxsU-nkBUk%23t%3D25s&d=DLcSJ3at4d3q9zJfdG0PmZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=6a2505fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sSxsU-nkBUk#t=25s</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40f9a99c6326608646218d9e56d7cbc51af31cc","tid":467983,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:37:01.000Z","msg":"點解人地中場休息咁正, 香港咁悶?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gDKMSGb5Zkk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgDKMSGb5Zkk&d=DLcSJ3at4d3q9zJfdG0PmZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a336f9cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gDKMSGb5Zkk</a>"},{"pid":"25d40f1fe1736c43272af5da7ccb90f123607995","tid":467983,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:40:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">金帥重召羅素串演中鋒  港隊秘密武器「黎」料</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171111/large/11s6-401pzok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171111%2Flarge%2F11s6-401pzok.jpg&h=b3039591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周二晚在大球場上演的亞洲盃第三圈外圍賽，迎戰黎巴嫩的爭出線關鍵戰準備。獲港足主教練金判坤重召入隊的和富大埔中堅羅素，將是挑戰勁敵黎巴嫩的「秘密武器」，因為港隊已部署必要時將這名身高達1米90的入籍兵推前串演中鋒。<br />\n<br />\n世界排名142位的港足前晚在旺角場約2,500名球迷面前，強陣友賽排名125的巴林，由於此戰是對亞盃外B組榜首黎巴嫩前的最後測試機會，故金帥排出強陣應戰，防線則有獲重召的羅素替羅拔圖，其餘佐迪、丹尼、徐德帥及麥基等都是上仗擊敗馬來西亞的主力，當中以黃洋帶領陳俊樂及黃威的中場鐵三角，成功串連攻守，且甚具效率。<br />\n<br />\n港隊下半場開始作出調動，戰至60分鐘陸續換出佐迪、黃洋、黃威及丹尼等正選，尾段連失兩球致敗，值得注意是教練金判坤上下半場都曾嘗試將入籍兵羅素推上最前串演中鋒，他賽後指這是球隊的戰術部署：「上半場測試球隊戰術，算是成功的，下半場開始換走部份主力，希望保護這些球員以免受傷。至於中堅羅素在上、下半場尾段被推到最前串演中鋒，是想在實戰中觀察效果。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">望勝黎巴嫩主導形勢</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，金判坤表示未來會讓更多年輕小將如鄭展龍等上場，吸收更多國際賽經驗，為港隊未來接班鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n由於港隊出線的形勢會受到同組北韓對馬來西亞兩場的賽果影響，不過，如港隊對黎巴嫩能夠全取三分，在最後一場外圍賽作客北韓可主導形勢，故對黎巴嫩的目標定是全取三分，而對巴林嘗試在尾段安排港隊身形最高大的羅素推前，演練空襲的效果；惟對黎巴嫩是安排他正選，還是擔當後備「秘密武器」，有待操練後決定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171111/large/aa0601a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171111%2Flarge%2Faa0601a.gif&h=d600d653&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c866b9bf165e4bd7f48c028ebb07e17ca431fbcc","tid":467983,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T05:41:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電視有冇直播?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nVIUTV 96"},{"pid":"3f20ea7